TopicTitle: Quick Question on Vanilla Part Information

Articles.Content:
Hey guys. I was checking the wiki for information on parts, and it seems really outdated:

http://kerbalspaceprogram.com/~kerbalsp/wiki/index.php?title=Parts

Do we have anything with this information, but applicable to .16?

I'm trying to make a T:W excel spreadsheet.

Thanks for the help!

That is the old wiki, which hasn't been updated since Jan 2012, as the result of impossible amounts of spamming and vandalism.

The new wiki is HERE. Its part list is much more up-to-date.
Any chance the old wiki could be deleted or something? It is annoying in that it comes up first when searching on google for the kerbal wiki.
I agree. It took me awhile to figure out where the correct wiki was.
Just so people know, the correct wiki is in the light-blue navigation bar at the top of the forums.
